If you often e-mail the same
group of people, for example

ca33ff97-2f14-472b-9e89-8187cf07103b-1
00:00:03.494 --> 00:00:06.623
your team at work, instead of
having to Create an e-mail and

ca33ff97-2f14-472b-9e89-8187cf07103b-2
00:00:06.623 --> 00:00:09.290
adding each person as a
recipient individually each

ca33ff97-2f14-472b-9e89-8187cf07103b-3
00:00:09.290 --> 00:00:11.239
time, you can create a contact
group.

c44d9dc2-d666-450a-98e8-ab947e530786-0
00:00:11.640 --> 00:00:14.290
So you'll only need to type the
groups name to e-mail everyone

c44d9dc2-d666-450a-98e8-ab947e530786-1
00:00:14.290 --> 00:00:14.880
in that group.

