To do this in Microsoft Outlook,
start by going to your contacts

fc0e64ea-1e4e-4b66-afc6-5c2f44594d1f-1
00:00:19.538 --> 00:00:22.860
by clicking the People button
here in the navigation bar and

fc0e64ea-1e4e-4b66-afc6-5c2f44594d1f-2
00:00:22.860 --> 00:00:25.908
with the Home tab selected,
click the arrow next to New

fc0e64ea-1e4e-4b66-afc6-5c2f44594d1f-3
00:00:25.908 --> 00:00:27.760
Contact and choose Contact
Group.

2fdc7558-cdb9-4d53-a866-aeeb5761f8cd-0
00:00:28.610 --> 00:00:30.930
In this window that opens, enter
a name for the group.

